lines.text: They call me Numbers here. 3 to 1 says you can guess why.
Ten to one says I don't give a rat's butt.
Now, I don't have to tell you that jerks like that have been dumping their garbage on us for years. Uh, well, I guess I just did, huh.
I'm, ah, tryin' to get the girl.
You and every other beau in this camp. Christine would chew you up and spit you out like bad jerky, even before you asked her out.
Well, I figure if you ain't ratted on me yet, then ya must be an all-right brother.
Man, I got a sister in Georgia and three brothers in Jersey! You ain't my "brother"!
Well, homey, I gotta jet, so ya know, I'll talk wit ya later, yo?
Got to jet, sir. Of course. Yo.
We don't... disturb... the artist... when... the artist... is working!
